FX/Treasury Sales - Singapore
Location:  Singapore
Salary:  SGD180000 - SGD200000 per annum + Bonus & BenefitsA global software solution provider to the financial services industry is looking to hire a senior sales manager to based in Singapore on a permanent basis. You will be responsible for selling the companies Treasury and FX product to sell side and buy side institutions in South East Asia.
My client is looking specifically to hire a candidate with experience working in an FX or Treasury sales role for a bank. My client can offer an extremely competitive salary as well as an aggressive bonus structure on top of an excellent benefits package.
If you are currently working or have previously worked for a bank in an FX or Treasury sales role and would be interested in taking on a new challenge please apply with your most recent CV.
